所有智慧電燈<br />\n8、要有真雙普選</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以上訴求全部掛勾，唔係選擇題，缺一不可<br />\n如果政府係聽日記者會再無回應，<strong>8月10號，行動全面升級</strong>"},{"pid":"45eb8dac8daf2093b15abf5f07211657b7874565","tid":1410620,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:16:05.000Z","msg":"四天工作週<br />\n全世界工人權益最前線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c5be433c775decca48546f663b977821c8335e","tid":1410620,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:18:25.000Z","msg":"霸收費站，免費俾車過"},{"pid":"29385a00437796f3a33f3090b81c601e51b72124","tid":1410620,"uid":141508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b04a336b807db111140210fc10d02a81e30a3d4","tid":1410620,"uid":4539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:54:31.000Z","msg":"有無辦法令股市開唔成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:18:32.000Z","msg":"令將軍澳個資訊中心失靈"},{"pid":"67b720f15a5225604027d6ba14d3496e9547e5de","tid":1410620,"uid":280230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:19:31.000Z","msg":"收費亭收皮就得，有冇電腦高手"},{"pid":"36eb869d08a00fb64d6e9ce6eb286493ee61dd3a","tid":1410620,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162d24daea8cd9a2e9a8a4c059c4b591e744a923","tid":1410620,"uid":9448,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"39b73f13af0365f139258deb45db38288bbae7bf","tid":1410620,"uid":141508,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:23:07.000Z","msg":"中共要面，搵一小隊打爆香港回歸祖國紀念碑，江澤民題字都唔要，比燒七七七支旗更有效"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df93b485c3986359d6b1ae2fedea0f7e0335d361","tid":1410620,"uid":278922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"搞有錢佬先有用，遊行傳統豪宅區，睇